apps.mtdesktop.tabletop
Interface TabletopContentManager.DesktopKeyboardListener

All Known Implementing Classes:
MultiUserNotepad
Enclosing class:
TabletopContentManager
public static interface TabletopContentManager.DesktopKeyboardListener

The listener interface for receiving desktopKeyboard events. The class that is interested in processing a desktopKeyboard event implements this interface, and the object created with that class is registered with a component using the component's addDesktopKeyboardListener method. When the desktopKeyboard event occurs, that object's appropriate method is invoked.

See Also:
DesktopKeyboardEvent
